text: The Mandi Lamb rice is superb, the meat is soft and delicious. My kids love the Pide Turkish Pizza Cheese and lastly not need to go to Arab st to get Kunafe, you can get it at Kebabwala, thumbs up!!! Overall my family love the food!!!

Great dining  experience at KEBABWALA . The food was flavourful and authentic, with standout dishes like Lamb Mandi Rice, Chicken Kebab, Kunafe and etc. The atmosphere was inviting, and the service was friendly. Highly recommend!
